snippet.title: Catalyst Black - Pre-Alpha
snippet.description:
Catalyst Black is the new team-based, battleground shooter coming from Super Evil Megacorp (makers of Vainglory). All game footage seen here is early, pre-Alpha.


Stay in touch via our social channels, and become a founder in our Discord!

YouTube: https://www.youtube.com/c/CatalystBlack
Discord: http://discord.gg/catalystblack
Twitter: http://twitter.com/catalystblk
Facebook: http://facebook.com/catalystblack
Instagram: http://instagram.com/catalystblackgame

http://superevilmegacorp.com

Never settle for the lesser evil.
